// OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Flow with PKCE for React SPA
// NOTE: Implicit flow (response_type=token) is deprecated and insecure.
// Using Authorization Code Flow with PKCE instead, which is the recommended
// approach for SPAs per OAuth 2.0 Security Best Current Practice (RFC 9700).

